{"body": "I prefer the json-mimicry of 1.9 hashes, but in this case you're binding to a specific runtime version at the wrong time. And you don't get the enjoyment of writing \"key: val\" as it is being written for you.\r\n\r\nLet the developer choose to bind to 1.9 by using the new hash syntax in their own code, not the framework generated code.\r\n\r\nThank you for ```--old-style-hash``` - while it doesn't help ex post facto, I have added it to my template for future projects.", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/1275239", "created_at": "2011-06-01T15:56:02Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/1213#issuecomment-1275239", "updated_at": "2011-06-01T15:56:02Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 1213, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/defeated/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/defeated/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/defeated/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/defeated", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/defeated/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/defeated", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/defeated/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://2.gravatar.com/avatar/648805ae18e92b7c71e46f3caa23ddc8?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F44968aece94f667e4095002d140b5896.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/defeated/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/defeated/received_events", "gravatar_id": "648805ae18e92b7c71e46f3caa23ddc8", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/defeated/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "defeated", "type": "User", "id": 1920, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/defeated/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "52385b8dbd3543c151011e53"}, "id": 1275239, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/1213"}
